@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kaptos(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.abs(v0) * wp.cos(wp.exp(v1 + 0.15)))
    v0 = wp.cos(v1)
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.14) + (v1 + 0.25 + v0 + 0.45)) * 0.33)
    v1 = v1
    tmp = (0.64 + wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 0.65)))
    v1 = wp.exp(((v2 + 0.07 - v0 + 0.75) - wp.cos(v1 + 0.94)))
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.abs(v2 + 0.21)) / (wp.sin(tmp + 0.41) * 0.44))
    data[tid] = v0
